Package: ellmer.extensions
Title: Groq and Gemini Provider Extensions for ellmer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Xavier", "Marquez", , "marquez.x@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides ellmer provider extensions with full support for Groq
    structured outputs, batch processing, and parallel execution, plus Gemini
    file-based batch chat support. Extends ellmer provider classes to add
    provider-specific batch semantics and compatibility behaviors.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
